{"title":"Overall","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Overall","format":"html"},"headingText":"Key indicators","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{r}\nsource(\"R/data_setup.R\")\n```\n\nThis dashboard summarizes ASQ-3 Saudi results and is organized in the left sidebar.\nUse **Overall** for sample-level indicators and trends by questionnaire month (`quest`), **Descriptive statistics** to build custom Table 1 outputs, and **Psychometric results** to review reliability estimates across domains and questionnaires.\n\n\n```{r}\nknitr::kable(overall_summary, caption = \"Project-level overview\")\n```\n\n## Records by questionnaire (`quest`)\n\n```{r}\nknitr::kable(quest_counts, caption = \"N by ASQ-3 questionnaire month\")\n```\n\n```{r}\nggplot(quest_counts, aes(x = factor(quest), y = n)) +\n  geom_col(fill = \"#1F6AA5\") +\n  labs(x = \"Questionnaire month (quest)\", y = \"N\", title = \"Sample size by questionnaire\") +\n  theme_minimal(base_size = 12)\n```\n\n## Domain means by `quest`\n\n```{r}\nggplot(domain_summary_long, aes(x = quest, y = mean_score, color = domain)) +\n  geom_line(linewidth = 1) +\n  geom_point(size = 2) +\n  scale_x_continuous(breaks = sort(unique(domain_summary_long$quest))) +\n  labs(x = \"Questionnaire month (quest)\", y = \"Mean domain score\", color = \"Domain\") +\n  theme_minimal(base_size = 12)\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{r}\nsource(\"R/data_setup.R\")\n```\n\nThis dashboard summarizes ASQ-3 Saudi results and is organized in the left sidebar.\nUse **Overall** for sample-level indicators and trends by questionnaire month (`quest`), **Descriptive statistics** to build custom Table 1 outputs, and **Psychometric results** to review reliability estimates across domains and questionnaires.\n\n## Key indicators\n\n```{r}\nknitr::kable(overall_summary, caption = \"Project-level overview\")\n```\n\n## Records by questionnaire (`quest`)\n\n```{r}\nknitr::kable(quest_counts, caption = \"N by ASQ-3 questionnaire month\")\n```\n\n```{r}\nggplot(quest_counts, aes(x = factor(quest), y = n)) +\n  geom_col(fill = \"#1F6AA5\") +\n  labs(x = \"Questionnaire month (quest)\", y = \"N\", title = \"Sample size by questionnaire\") +\n  theme_minimal(base_size = 12)\n```\n\n## Domain means by `quest`\n\n```{r}\nggplot(domain_summary_long, aes(x = quest, y = mean_score, color = domain)) +\n  geom_line(linewidth = 1) +\n  geom_point(size = 2) +\n  scale_x_continuous(breaks = sort(unique(domain_summary_long$quest))) +\n  labs(x = \"Questionnaire month (quest)\", y = \"Mean domain score\", color = \"Domain\") +\n  theme_minimal(base_size = 12)\n```\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":true,"echo":false,"output":true,"warning":false,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"message":false,"engine":"knitr"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeindex","latex-makeindex-opts":[],"latex-tlmgr-opts":[],"latex-input-paths":[],"latex-output-dir":null,"link-external-icon":false,"link-external-newwindow":false,"self-contained-math":false,"format-resources":[],"notebook-links":true},"pandoc":{"standalone":true,"wrap":"none","default-image-extension":"png","to":"html","toc":false,"css":["l